main event: A civilian observed a round-shaped orange colored object while driving in Winter Park, Florida, on November 16, 1966.
interesting points: The object was observed for 3 minutes and moved down then up,The investigator believed it was a reflection in the witness's windshield,The witness was nervous during questioning and had detailed observations,The witness did not believe in flying saucers,The sighting occurred at approximately 2:30 AM.
witness description: Mrs. [redacted], returning home in her car.
